{"name":"Experience Letter","owner":"Administrator","creation":"2025-09-03 23:56:20.405463","modified":"2025-09-05 00:12:22.167177","modified_by":"Administrator","docstatus":0,"idx":0,"doc_type":"Employee","module":"HR","default_print_language":"en","standard":"No","custom_format":1,"disabled":0,"print_format_type":"Jinja","raw_printing":0,"html":"<div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;\">\n    <!-- Logo on the left -->\n    <div>\n        <img src=\"/files/girman.jpeg\" alt=\"Company Logo\" style=\"height: 60px;\">\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Company Name on the right -->\n    <div style=\"text-align: right;\">\n        <h2 style=\"margin: 0;\">Girman Technologies</h2>\n        <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #555;\">Innovating the Future</p>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n<hr style=\"margin: 20px 0; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">\n\n<!-- Title -->\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px;\">Experience Letter</h3>\n\n<!-- Body -->\n<p>Date: {{ frappe.utils.formatdate(frappe.utils.nowdate()) }}</p>\n<p>To Whomsoever It May Concern,</p>\n\n<p>\nThis is to certify that <b>{{ doc.employee_name }}</b>, who joined Girman Technologies on \n<b>{{ frappe.utils.formatdate(doc.date_of_joining) }}</b>, was employed with us until \n<b>{{ frappe.utils.formatdate(doc.relieving_date) if doc.relieving_date else \"Present\" }}</b>.\n</p>\n\n<p>\nDuring their tenure, {{ doc.employee_name }} held the position of <b>{{ doc.designation }}</b> in the \n<b>{{ doc.department }}</b> department. They demonstrated professionalism, dedication, and competence in all their responsibilities.\n</p>\n\n<p>We sincerely wish them continued success and growth in their future endeavors.</p>\n\n<br><br><br>\n<p><b>Authorized Signatory</b></p>\n","raw_commands":null,"margin_top":15,"margin_bottom":15,"margin_left":15,"margin_right":15,"align_labels_right":0,"show_section_headings":0,"line_breaks":0,"absolute_value":0,"font_size":14,"font":null,"page_number":"Hide","css":null,"format_data":null,"print_format_builder":0,"print_format_builder_beta":0}